scripts.build: npm run build-es6 && npm run build-amd && npm run build-node && npm run build-global
scripts.build-global: mkdir -p dist/global && browserify dist/node/all.js -d -p [minifyify --map dist/global/paths.js.map --output dist/global/paths.js.map] -o dist/global/paths.js
